title: Dr. Robert Kadlec, HHS Preparedness and Response

Guests: Dr. Robert Kadlec, Assistant Secretary for Preparedness and Response at the U.S. Department of Health & Human Services, Tim Kelly, election strategist and owner of Kelly Strategy, and Congressman Andy Barr, a Republican representing Kentucky’s 6th district.
